@lib go 0.8

# Source purpose: reusable Go engineering rules.
# Official raw URL: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/KakunynQA/ail-spec/main/libs/go.lib.ail

M use gofmt
M run go test when logic changes
M preserve pub api and obs behavior
M use ctx correctly
M handle err explicitly
B deps without strong reason
B large rewrite without clear gain
P idiomatic go simple readable
P small reversible patches
C alloc loops locks ctx goroutines err handling package boundaries tests coverage
X go test ./...
X go vet ./...
